@node reqtools "ReqTools"

PlusEd is using ReqTools.library. @{b}ReqTools is copyrighted © Nico François.@{ub}
Version 2.1a is distributed with this version of PlusEd. All necessary
files can be found in the directory 'ReqTools'.
@endnode



@node techstuff "Technical stuff"

PlusEd was compiled with SAS/C 6.10. The GUI was created with PowerSource
(the main window) and GadToolsBox 1.4 (the additional windows and the
menus), both written by Jan van den Baard.
@endnode



